reviewText: Brought this Movie and at first I had a hiccup playing it on my DVD player but I put it in my computer and it plays great and it is very clear and I Love this movie.

The best movie I have ever seen on the life
of Jesus , highly recommended.

I LOVE this movie! I watch it, at the very least, around Easter every year and sometimes in between. Though it says it's Region 2, I've not had any trouble playing it in DVD players or my laptop. So don't let that stop you from getting it.
